homesick /ˈhəʊmˌsɪk/

1. ADJ If you are homesick , you feel unhappy because you are away from home and are missing your family, friends, and home very much. 想家的 

例： She's feeling a little homesick. 她感到有些想家了。 

2. homesickness N-UNCOUNT 想家 

例： There were inevitable bouts of homesickness. 难免会生出一阵阵思乡之情。

